# ── NOT ignored (kept on purpose) ──────────────────────
# site/ is the built, self-contained website and IS committed —
# it cannot be regenerated from this repo alone (the build script
# lives outside it), so everything under site/ (including the
# assets/*.min.js libraries and generated *-data.js / search-index.js)
# must stay tracked. Do not add site/ here.
